    "dialogue":{
        "init":[
            {
                "type":"select",
                "char":"Shopkeeper",
                "expression":"Neutral",
                "diag":"What's up?",
                "timeout":60,
                "linkto":[
                    "option1",
                    "option2",
                    "option3"
                ]
            }
        ],
        "option1":[
            "Where are we?",
            {
                "type":"default",
                "char":"Shopkeeper",
                "expression":"Unamused",
                "diag":"... Guy. We're in the Thicklet. You live [I]five minutes[I]away from it.",
                "timeout":60
            },
            {
                "type":"default",
                "char":"Guy",
                "expression":"Unamused",
                "diag":"Of course I know that, but [I]where[I] in the Thicklet are we?",
                "timeout":60
            },
            {
                "type":"default",
                "char":"Shopkeeper",
                "expression":"Curious",
                "diag":"I don't actually know, but it isn't on any maps I've seen of the island.",
                "timeout":60
            },
            {
                "type":"default",
                "char":"Guy",
                "expression":"Weirded",
                "diag":"That's. Um. Worrying. Do you have supplies for the night...?",
                "timeout":60
            },
            {
                "type":"default",
                "char":"Shopkeeper",
                "expression":"Neutral",
                "diag":"No need to ask, as long as you have Nuggets. And considering that machine there basically allows for Nugget farming...",
                "timeout":60
            }
        ],
        "option2":[
            "It's funny we use Nuggets as cash.",
            {
                "type":"default",
                "char":"Guy",
                "expression":"Happy",
                "diag":"Didn't the Ancestors use to call some food made outta bird like that?",
                "timeout":60
            },
            {
                "type":"default",
                "char":"Shopkeeper",
                "expression":"Unamused",
                "diag":"Yes, but they also called bits of metal like that, and as you can see, these are bits of Portal. That's why we call them the same way.",
                "timeout":60
            },
            {
                "type":"default",
                "char":"Guy",
                "expression":"Neutral",
                "diag":"Oh.",
                "timeout":60
            },
            {
                "type":"default",
                "char":"Guy",
                "expression":"Happy",
                "diag":"That's interesting!",
                "timeout":60
            },
                        {
                "type":"default",
                "char":"Shopkeeper",
                "expression":"Unamused",
                "diag":"It would be if we kept pre-war writings. We didn't, so we have no idea why that was.",
                "timeout":60
            }
        ],
        "option3":[
            "How does the Wave Machine work?",
            {
                "type":"default",
                "char":"Guy",
                "expression":"Angry",
                "diag":"And why does it even exist, actually. Who'd make that.",
                "timeout":60
            },
            {
                "type":"default",
                "char":"Shopkeeper",
                "expression":"Happy",
                "diag":"Someone who knows the way to my gratitude! Infinite money!",
                "timeout":60
            },
            {
                "type":"default",
                "char":"Guy",
                "expression":"Unamused",
                "diag":"... of course. Any [B]actual[N] knowledge of its inner workings?",
                "timeout":60
            },
            {
                "type":"default",
                "char":"Shopkeeper",
                "expression":"Curious",
                "diag":"Wave difficulty seems to be consistent even if payouts aren't. Though harder opponents do give out more cash.",
                "timeout":60
            },
            {
                "type":"default",
                "char":"Shopkeeper",
                "expression":"Unamused",
                "diag":"Here's a tip - go and buy things from me. You aren't going to kill any monster with your bare fists.",
                "timeout":60
            }
        ]
    }
